title: FULL SHOW: We Talk Rihanna At Halftime 2023, Chat With Doechii, and Talk Fake Prince's
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Talk Rihanna At Halftime 2023, Chat With Doechii, and Talk Fake Prince's
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we talk about the announcement that shook us which is Rihanna will be performing at the 2023 Superbowl Halftime Show! Later on we chat with TDE rapper, Doechii, about her journey, overcoming bullying, and everything "she/her/black b*tch". Charlamagne also gives his Donkey to a Prince..... Oh did we mention he's not a Prince?

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
